#Wien Bridge Oscillator

##Schematic & PCB
Full schematic and simulation is available in the 'Wien_oscillator' file in LTSpice.
The PCB can be accessed using a proper PCB design software and accessing the 'oscilatorWien3.brd' file.
The circuit was simulated in LTSpice and routed in OrCAD.

## Documentation
Full project documentation (schematic, simulation results, design decisions) is available in 'DOC.pdf'.

## Gerber Files
Fabrication-ready files are in the `/Layout` folder.
